refentry.refsect1:
  &reftitle.description;

   booltouch
   stringfilename
   inttime
   intatime



   尝试将由 filename
   给出的文件的访问和修改时间设定为给出的时间。如果没有给出可选参数
   time，则使用当前系统时间。如果给出了第三个参数
   atime，则给定文件的访问时间会被设为
   atime。注意访问时间总是会被修改的，不论有几个参数。



   如果文件不存在，则会被创建。&return.success;




    touch 例子


<?php
if (touch($FileName)) {
    echo "$FileName modification time has been changed to present time";
} else {
    echo "Sorry, could not change modification time of $FileName";
}
?>

&reftitle.changelog;







     &Version;
     &Description;





     5.3.0

      It became possible to change the modification time of a directory 
      under Windows.

  &reftitle.examples;



    touch example


<?php
if (touch($filename)) {
    echo $filename . ' modification time has been changed to present time';
} else {
    echo 'Sorry, could not change modification time of ' . $filename;
}
?>







    touch using the time parameter


<?php
// This is the touch time, we'll set it to one hour in the past.
$time = time() - 3600;

// Touch the file
if (!touch('some_file.txt', $time)) {
    echo 'Whoops, something went wrong...';
} else {
    echo 'Touched file with success';
}
?>

&reftitle.notes;
&note.filesystem-time-res;



  Prior to PHP 5.3.0 it was not possible to change the modification time 
  of a directory with this function under Windows.
